# Content display mode in the Flow

***Choose your display mode***

---

This SmartApp offers two different types of content display in the ***Flow*** for you to choose from. The ***Flow*** is the place in the application in which users see and react to other users' created content, you can choose to display it as a ***stack*** of cards in which you can navigate by swiping on your screen (see first screenshot) or as a ***list*** on which you scroll up and down (see second screenshot).<br>
This choice is totally depending on your preferences, our preference is for the cards display as it is, we think, a more interactive and interesting way to navigate through the content!
